---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="關於這個網站">
  <section class="about">
    <p class="eyebrow">About the Project</p>
    <h1>關於這個網站</h1>

    <section class="about-block">
      <h2>我是肉丸七</h2>

      <p class="lead">
        這裡不只是肉丸七日記的內容集合，而是一個隨著時間慢慢展開的內容空間。
      </p>

      <p class="story">
        我叫肉丸七。
        我住在肉丸宮，和一群朋友一起生活。有大粉兔、小粉兔，有小小的Boo，還有幾個你以後會慢慢認識的傢伙。我們就這樣，住在一起，過日子。
        我不是什麼特別的熊。
        有時候我會戴上墨鏡。不是因為很酷，是因為那天需要一層東西擋在我和這個世界之間。但不是每天都這樣，有些日子，我就這樣走出去了。
        我開始寫日記。把每天看見的、感覺到的、還沒想清楚的，慢慢寫下來。不急，不趕，有時候一篇日記只是一個下午的光，或是Boo睡著的樣子。
        人生走到某個地方，你會開始想好好記錄它。這裡就是我記錄的地方。
        歡迎你坐下來，一起慢慢看。
      </p>

      <div class="lang-divider"></div>

      <p class="lead en-lead">
        This is more than just random notes. It's a space that slowly unfolds
        over time.
      </p>

      <p class="story">
        My name is Bearball Seven. I live in Bearball Studio, together with a
        bunch of friends — Big Pink Rabbit, Little Pink Rabbit, tiny Boo Bear,
        and a few others you'll get to know gradually. We share a space, share
        some days, and get by together. I'm not a particularly special bear.
        Sometimes I wear sunglasses. Not because I'm cool — but because some
        days I need something between me and the world. A little distance. A
        little shield. But not every day. Some days I just walk out without
        them. I started keeping a journal. Writing down the things I notice, the
        things I feel, the things I haven't quite sorted out yet. No rush.
        Sometimes an entry is just the light of one afternoon, or the way Boo
        looks when he's fallen asleep. There comes a point in life when you want
        to start remembering it properly. This is where I do that. Pull up a
        chair. Stay a while.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="about-block">
      <h2>關於 Autumnreal Lab</h2>

      <p>
        Autumnreal Lab 是這一切背後的起點。
        內容、設計與創作思考在此交織，關心的不只是作品本身，
        更在於那些被理解、被感受的瞬間，以及時間如何讓一切慢慢沉澱。
      </p>

      <p class="quote">
        Concepts Shaped, Creative Journeys Told.<br />
        在這裡，內容編織成精彩故事。
      </p>

      <p>
        從文章到觀點，從角色創作到品牌實驗，
        這裡逐步累積成一個屬於自己的內容世界，
        讓創作以一種長期而自然的節奏延續下去。
      </p>

      <div class="lang-divider"></div>

      <h3>About Autumnreal Lab</h3>

      <p>
        Autumnreal Lab is the creative origin behind it all. It brings together
        content, design, and creative thinking, with attention not only to what
        is made, but also to how it is understood, felt, and slowly shaped over
        time.
      </p>

      <p class="quote">
        Concepts Shaped, Creative Journeys Told.<br />
        Where ideas become stories.
      </p>

      <p>
        From writing and reflection to character creation and brand exploration,
        this space gradually forms a world of its own, where creative work
        continues as a long-term and natural rhythm.
      </p>
    </section>

    <p class="ig-wrap">
      href="https://www.instagram.com/bearball.seven/" target="_blank"
      rel="noopener noreferrer" class="ig-link" > Follow → @bearball.seven
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about {
    max-width: 680px;
  }

  .eyebrow {
    margin: 0 0 10px;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #8a8a8a;
  }

  .about h1 {
    margin: 0 0 24px;
    font-size: 2.6rem;
    line-height: 1.2;
    color: #13335f;
  }

  .about-block {
    margin-bottom: 56px;
  }

  .about h2 {
    margin: 0 0 18px;
    font-size: 1.55rem;
    line-height: 1.4;
    color: #13335f;
  }

  .about h3 {
    margin: 0 0 18px;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    line-height: 1.4;
    color: #13335f;
  }

  .lead {
    margin: 0 0 18px;
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    line-height: 1.9;
    color: #2f2f2f;
  }

  .en-lead {
    color: #2f2f2f;
  }

  .about p {
    max-width: 640px;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.95;
    color: #444;
  }

  .story {
    white-space: pre-line;
  }

  .quote {
    margin: 28px 0;
    padding-left: 18px;
    border-left: 3px solid #d7deea;
    color: #13335f;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .lang-divider {
    width: 100%;
    height: 1px;
    margin: 36px 0 28px;
    background: #e6e6e6;
  }

  .ig-wrap {
    margin-top: 12px;
  }

  .ig-link {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 10px 16px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: #13335f;
    color: white;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .ig-link:hover {
    opacity: 0.9;
  }
</style>
